data.description: Reduced Price!  Now you can look forward to going home at the end of a long day :)  A beautifully well-maintained 2 story house plan with the main living spaces like the living room, dinning room and the kitchen and a half bathroom, etc. are on the main level, while all three bedrooms, full bathroom and washer/dryer are located upstairs. In addition to this home is a spacious sunroom that leads to the outdoor red brick walk way and a decorative man-made gazebo with plenty of assorted landscape and shady trees. So many other fine details and upgrades were put together by the owners.  Don't miss out, schedule your showing today for more information on this awesome home.  ;)
